HEADWORD: Riparian
<hw>Ri*pa"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>riparius</ets>, fr. <ets>ripa</ets> a bank. See <er>River</er>, and
cf. <er>Arrive</er>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to the bank of a
river; <as>as, <ex>riparian</ex> rights</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
